Key Match Events: Budu Zivzivadze scored a brace for Georgia
Maxime Chanot received a straight red card for Luxembourg
Miscellaneous Highlights: Georgia booked their place in the Euro 2024 playoff finals
Luxembourg crashed out of contention to qualify for their first-ever major tournament
Others: Georgia exerted their influence from the outset
Luxembourg succumbed to the Crusaders before the interval
Georgia will march on to face either Greece or Kazakhstan early next week for a place in Germany
